                        <li>Our legitimate interest in operating and improving the website</li>
                        <li>Compliance with legal obligations</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>We retain personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in
                        this Privacy Policy.</p>
                    <p>If you are a resident of the European Economic Area (EEA), you have certain data protection
                        rights, including:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>The right to access, update, or delete your personal information</li>
                        <li>The right to correct inaccurate information</li>
                        <li>The right to object to processing</li>
                        <li>The right to restrict processing</li>
                        <li>The right to data portability</li>
                        <li>The right to withdraw consent</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>You may contact us to exercise any of these rights.
                    </p>
                </section>
